  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About:</h2>In Tiny Toy Tanks you are in control of a small blue tank. Your Goal is to destroy all the opposing tanks in 40+ hand crafted levels. Opposing tanks have different AI with different strengths and weaknesses. Moreover, every level has many other mechanics like TNT, Magnets and more.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Tanks</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452850/extras/39d695e2e2b9843a5c96eba6e52bc756.avif?t=1627988529\" width=132 height=94 /></span> Player controlled it can turbo and lay mines.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452850/extras/f1e8f747c797ff522cb888dd0dc5c4ce.avif?t=1627988529\" width=132 height=94 /></span> <strong> Brown Tanks </strong> Attack speed is slow and does not move<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452850/extras/5fd3d84d14e855b088f3e6b6557a1910.avif?t=1627988529\" width=132 height=94 /></span> <strong> Gray Tanks </strong> Attack speed is slow and can move<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452850/extras/7f4853fc8b707a87966945560f0f8adf.avif?t=1627988529\" width=132 height=94 /></span> <strong> Blue Tanks </strong> High-speed rockets<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452850/extras/fdf90f866439eab6d13e24d59a47acc6.avif?t=1627988529\" width=132 height=94 /></span> <strong> Yellow Tanks </strong> Can place mines<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452850/extras/179da4782bbdcf0009df933de6285239.avif?t=1627988529\" width=132 height=94 /></span> <strong> Green Tanks </strong> Super aim technology<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452850/extras/fd845bdfd0e8e56b7527f9d9041e98e4.avif?t=1627988529\" width=132 height=94 /></span> <strong>Red Tanks </strong> Large number of rockets<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1452850/extras/82f65c94887d9d66554bb1ee2a929caa.avif?t=1627988529\" width=132 height=94 /></span> <strong>Purple Tanks </strong> Evasion technology",
